9
00:01:56,360 --> 00:02:00,600
A: I'm still working on it.  M: I'm still working on it.

10
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:02,520
A: I'm still working on it.

11
00:02:02,520 --> 00:02:09,200
M: Why don't we listen to some other examples on how you can use this word and then  we'll come back and explain it?   

12
