A: So, that's basically America's fast food.  M: Yeah. Burger, coke and fries.

18
00:03:03,920 --> 00:03:10,480
A: Okay. M: Hehe. A: What's next on the menu?   M: On the menu we have a complementary glass of wine. 

19
00:03:10,480 --> 00:03:15,640
A: Complementary glass of wine. M: Complementary glass of wine.

20
00:03:15,640 --> 00:03:23,160
A: Complementary means…  M: That it's free.  A: Free.  M: Yes.  A: We love that, ha?  M: Yeah, we definitely like free things

21
00:03:23,160 --> 00:03:30,280
A: Well, um, I have another one for us here, another interesting phrase – I'll go with.  M: I'll go with. 

22
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:33,480
A: I'll go with.

23
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:40,040
A: So, basically, it's another way of saying “I'm choosing".   M: Yeah, I'll choose or I'll take. 

24
00:03:40,080 --> 00:03:46,200
A: Okay, very good.  M: Alright, the next word that I wanna take a look at is grab. 

25
